fields.label: Developer Options Instructions
fields.message:
Module Name: Primarily used for admin screen labeling. Container ID: Used for page section anchors, also possibly for developer code setup. CSS Classes: Use to add custom modifying classes, to alter the presentation of this section. Paste the desired classes in the CSS classes field (omit the quote marks!). Possible classes:
  • Text Color: add to affect text color in this section
    • 'text-color-primary'
    • 'text-color-secondary'
    • 'text-color-tertiary'
  • Background Color: add to affect background color
    • 'bg-color-primary'
    • 'bg-color-secondary'
    • 'bg-color-tertiary'
  • Spacing: we have inner & outer spacing classes, which will add space according to a number size 0-6. Add to all sides, or only top, bottom, left, or right.
    • Padding (inner spacing) - replace 'N' with a number size, 0-6
    • All Sides: 'p-N'
    • Top: 'p-t-N'
    • Bottom: 'p-b-N'
    • Left: 'p-l-N'
    • Right: 'p-r-N'
    • Margin (outer spacing) - replace 'N' with a number size, 0-6
    • All Sides: 'm-N'
    • Top: 'm-t-N'
    • Bottom: 'm-b-N'
    • Left: 'm-l-N'
    • Right: 'm-r-N'
